item.title: Knockout.js, jsRender, LESS, SquishIt
item.author: jkat98@gmail.com (Jason Krol)
item.description: This week was all about Knockout.js and my seemingly total lack of understanding of javascript and jquery! After struggling with Knockout (rather, struggling to implement it into an existing project that might be a little too complex for my first attempt with KO) I decided to back burner it for a while. However I did learn a lot more about dealing with data, json, and oop in general with javascript and jquery.
